Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是記錄媒體的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是舊式的 但應該沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以復原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許其中記錄著我們沒有見過的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 可以了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前不是說過會帶我參觀加爾剛蒂亞的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近哥很忙 沒這個閒工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 怎麼這麼說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都在火海中和我互許終生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,許個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 和你這種野蠻潑辣的妹子比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔端莊的小姐更是我的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著 拆除之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 映出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我們的機器還是第一次讀出如此詳細的數據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是設計圖 或者是操縱手冊嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人形機器人不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以技術水平來看 這東西和Chamber更為接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥機器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作這東西的人們走向了宇宙 並最終構築了銀河同盟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便離開了凍結的地球 他們仍舊沒有放棄鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然可悲 但這確實是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須從中吸取教訓 避免重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃午飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到庫蓋爾艦團上也有這麼棒的店舖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能消停點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這些料理加爾剛蒂亞上可都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也沒有點這麼多的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會負責吃光的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？啊…是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出遠門的時候我都會坐這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪真的很喜歡機械之類的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼歐都想把她挖走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候是情不自禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還去看了Chamber的駕駛艙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候…也是情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還開著潛水人形機器人去救雷德了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…別再說這個話題了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是大家太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的菜過會兒呈上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還打算吃那麼多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法跑來跑去和長時間運動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我天生心臟就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也沒法治療 所以我只能去適應它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有姐姐陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有醫生 雷德和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真堅強呢 貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你也很堅強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 你在一個陌生的地方開始了生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻像這樣交到了朋友 工作著 活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很弱小 但卻都很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 莉瑪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說要先回一趟自己的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是想要洗衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟今天天氣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也回去洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊抓捕對象 把他帶走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過了 我們的目的是讓雷德協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾到底有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能否駕馭這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不弄清楚 就無法將它用於戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的知識對我們而言是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用強只會適得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已在捕獲Striker駕駛員的行動中失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本國應該已經很不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的死亡是計劃之外的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下 應該認為新對象的出現是一個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得想辦法讓雷德自己離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的方針不變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果本國翻臉就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不單單是我們 就連這機體也保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你報告一下目前的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民們似乎相當勞累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為接收的前庫蓋爾艦團人員安排居住地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和維修船隻的工作還在繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物資不足這點也很讓人擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前幾天雖然從商船那裡補充了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因為人員增加 所以消費也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光只是時間問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零件和電池都搞不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各個公會都很頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長 希望你能採取一些對策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個地方 短缺的用品應該都可以得到補充
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說休閒設施也都很完善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艦團長莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事需要向大家宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始 加爾剛蒂亞將前往海上貨易據點 通稱龍宮城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 龍宮城是什麼地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請各船主們及各公會制定好物資採購計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時 我們也充分考慮了居民的慰勞問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龍宮城！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大規模的設施竟然能漂浮在海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 好多海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂 紗雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是第一次這麼近距離看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 玩個痛快吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝貝爾沒辦法來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麼大的地方逛來逛去 對他的身體負擔太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他說去幫奧爾德姆醫生調查東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給他買點禮物回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝各位提交計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會據此來進行貿易談判的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從同行那裡聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這裡鐵之類的物資好像全都漲價了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜種子和穀物好像也都被買斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說 我們出售的東西也可以賣個好價錢嘍？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就是行情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就乘機賺上一筆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 為什麼是這個時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和陸地的動向有關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和陸地有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳情還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以確定的是有部分物資流向了陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要時刻關注陸地各國的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他們接下來會有新的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和龍宮城高層見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會旁敲側擊一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 陸地嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相當可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們該怎麼辦 頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然對這遊樂園沒啥興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但調查一下也沒什麼壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像祭典一樣呢 莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 要試試看那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個去打想要的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個 像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑一個喜歡的打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是故意沒裝子彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海豚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 有好多的海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋哺乳動物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經離開海洋 後來又回到海中生活的物種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要選擇這樣的進化之路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到海中的牠們 現在到底在追求什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像可以和海豚一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和海豚…一起玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳裝都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳裝是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啦 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米也準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿內衣不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先去購物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件很適合莉瑪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 不錯 不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 這件如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面也有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人羨慕嫉妒恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得艾米他們真要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這麼開心的事我從來都沒有經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟你在那個庫蓋爾艦團嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼心事就和我們說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是同伴也是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想 要是能像那樣和哥哥一起玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原來有哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艦團上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長得帥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們所需要的物資 我們應該都能夠提供
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大艦團加爾剛蒂亞能停泊敝城 我們也是與有榮焉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們出售的商品也十分豐富 可以說是一次互惠互利的貿易
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分物資的流動存在偏向的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來只是我杞人憂天 這下心裡就踏實了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的消息還真是靈通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們而言 每一位客戶都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不會厚此薄彼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最新的世界地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面也標記了各勢力的分佈情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我們表示友好的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知幾位之後是否方便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必接受我們的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個好像不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著就像能做出各種各樣的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就選這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 你們都在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見啊 你們會來這種店舖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品味不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在給貝貝爾買禮物 正打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子們就老老實實地回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是大人的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的時間算什麼玩意兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢敗壞風氣 我可不會輕饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特船長…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防止居民給龍宮城添麻煩 我正在看守！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊…喝多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓她喝的啊！這樣子簡直太糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我們要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就兩個大老粗去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你說的 當然是現找一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 可以還給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛奪走的我的那顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這樣兒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 莉瑪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本國那邊已經開始做回收準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在部隊到達之前沒有達成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動就會被終止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 他們打算把馬茲爾也捨棄掉嗎？這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高機密的兵器不能再這樣放置於國外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面應該是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們最害怕的就是情報被洩露給敵國了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我想辦法壓下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一會兒就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機械自行解析並運用語言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是遺失的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會說話的機器…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像Chamber那樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是像他那樣的人工智能的前身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然連這種東西都造出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不更深入地和人類交流 就無法度過嚴酷的冰河期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人形機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是那個設計圖裡的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 我希望你能來我的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助我研究這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.14,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,檢測到了生命體反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾 我可能會讓你置身險境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.87,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像記錄中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 還是不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.94,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像記錄中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我無法理解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我開動了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有這一條路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的我卻開始討厭戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了？要單獨和我談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能幫我說服雷德 讓他離開加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我不懂 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然還有艾米和貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望雷德 艾米和貝貝爾跟我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去哪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？莉瑪你是陸地人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾米來的話 雷德肯定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是覺得不能丟下你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能離開加爾剛蒂亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝貝爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地上也許有辦法治好貝貝爾的病
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次見到陸地上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告訴過我 不要和陸地人有所瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到莉瑪是陸地人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.36,0:24:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使她說讓我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是移居到陌生的地方這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.59,0:24:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果能治好貝貝爾 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果治不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會讓那孩子陷入危險之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.14,0:24:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.17,0:24:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然變成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼辦啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.15,0:25:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4點鐘方向有艦團正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.78,0:25:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.26,0:25:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.18,0:25:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來沒有見過的船影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海賊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.58,0:25:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓護衛艦出動
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.36,0:26:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.32,0:26:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.46,0:26:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒趕上嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.67,0:26:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終究還是打算來硬的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不通知我們一聲就現身
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.21,0:26:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明已經把我們連同行動一起放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.16,0:26:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.09,0:26:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.63,0:26:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要抓到雷德 就是我們說的算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.14,0:26:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨棄掉莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.33,0:26:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出發
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告接近中的艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.79,0:26:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是加爾剛蒂亞艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.81,0:26:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告知貴艦團的所屬以及行動目的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.54,0:26:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長 那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.42,0:26:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好像不是海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.54,0:26:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛開始就一直以現在的距離和我們並行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.62,0:27:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.50,0:27:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的警戒對象都沒有裝備連接器
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.70,0:27:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥用的船隻…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.20,0:27:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝羅茲 這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.05,0:27:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.21,0:27:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 你知道什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.61,0:27:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在接近的艦團到底是什麼來歷？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.45,0:27:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是從陸地而來的特務艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.22,0:27:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.56,0:27:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前說過 陸地上也許能治好貝貝爾的病
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.95,0:27:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也會被迫過上比疾病更痛苦的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.88,0:27:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.07,0:27:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隱瞞了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.09,0:27:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.30,0:27:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是卡奇納斯號
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.34,0:27:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.54,0:27:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.03,0:27:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.70,0:27:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.56,0:27:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.88,0:27:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被突然出現的兩個男人抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.70,0:27:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自作主張！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.68,0:27:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.01,0:27:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.77,0:27:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在之前去過的那家食堂附近
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.69,0:28:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.63,0:28:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.42,0:28:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的目標是你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.68,0:28:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.82,0:28:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米是人質
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.01,0:28:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你被抓的話就無法回到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.09,0:28:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去說服他們把艾米帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.16,0:28:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.42,0:28:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄刻阿諾斯號 緊急聯絡！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:19.25,ruby,NTP,0,300,0,,Oceanus
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:19.25,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：希臘神話中大洋河的河神
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.91,0:28:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.30,0:28:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.88,0:28:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個有精神的小姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.82,0:28:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.20,0:28:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻釋放人質！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.82,0:28:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.35,0:28:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在可是我們的生命線
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.11,0:28:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以這女孩的生命為籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.47,0:29:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對象就會幫忙幫到底的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.35,0:29:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.77,0:29:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然特務艦隊已經現身
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.95,0:29:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就說明一切都遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.79,0:29:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃已經被放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.25,0:29:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼就是不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.78,0:29:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只管完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.78,0:29:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.53,0:29:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.05,0:29:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.57,0:29:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西果然不是人形機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.58,0:29:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 這到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稱他為強化外裝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:52.41,ruby,NTP,250,0,0,,Augmented body
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.02,0:29:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫馬茲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.80,0:29:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的同伴在駕駛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.26,0:29:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.95,0:30:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.20,0:30:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是同伴 是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.35,0:30:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.88,0:30:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.80,0:30:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.10,0:30:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對面來電
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.61,0:30:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本艦隊的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是殲滅正在脫離貴艦團的船舶 人員以及裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.10,0:30:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該船舶屬於我國
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望貴艦團不要進行妨礙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.30,0:30:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法認可
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.97,0:30:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩船上都確認到了本艦團的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.44,0:30:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請終止攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我國的正當權利 貴艦團已處在我軍的艦炮射程內
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.83,0:30:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.97,0:30:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴艦團的阻撓行為 我們將以武力加以排除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.83,0:30:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.22,0:30:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 不能放任居民的安全受到威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.31,0:31:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全艦做好攻擊準備 強化警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.35,0:31:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護衛艦請開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.31,0:31:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 乘上來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.76,0:31:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了艾米 我無論如何都必須保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.33,0:31:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.53,0:31:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想把你捲進陸地上已經歷時幾百年的國與國的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.79,0:31:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了獲取勝利 我曾想利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.69,0:31:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在我已經做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.59,0:31:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有權利破壞你們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.17,0:31:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.66,0:31:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乘上來！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.54,0:32:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非戰鬥人員請撤到艦團左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.86,0:32:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重複 非戰鬥人員請撤到艦團左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.46,0:32:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別推我！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.80,0:32:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別推！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.96,0:32:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.35,0:32:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人不在我們的射程內
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邊推進邊警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.22,0:32:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認到敵人大型艦開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各護衛艦 做好迎擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.36,0:32:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認兩側交差著彈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.71,0:32:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離已經被對方測量到了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.26,0:32:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.46,0:32:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.11,0:32:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護衛艦允許應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.83,0:33:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.41,0:33:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.72,0:33:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.98,0:33:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去避難！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.80,0:33:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.31,0:33:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:32.58,ruby,NTP,0,180,0,,Adios
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.14,0:33:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.76,0:33:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.20,0:33:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集情報辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.05,0:33:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜此所賜 我下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.68,0:33:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.62,0:34:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.11,0:34:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.28,0:34:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來沒見過這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.73,0:34:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西正在擴張控制系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.35,0:34:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.94,0:34:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.39,0:34:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前從來沒發生過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.26,0:34:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能開得動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.75,0:34:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.18,0:34:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像他的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.52,0:34:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.27,0:34:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在腦海裡描繪出你想做的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.18,0:34:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你想讓這傢伙做的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.72,0:34:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這東西的機制和Chamber一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.65,0:34:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他應該能領會的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.15,0:35:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛到那個地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.23,0:36:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.77,0:36:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保鏢工作關門大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.65,0:36:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去做海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.43,0:36:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在不想和陸地那邊扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.46,0:36:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 唯有這次不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.19,0:36:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬧個痛快 就當是離艦聲明了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.63,0:36:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.26,0:36:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別停歇！繼續開炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.63,0:36:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電磁兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.94,0:37:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.37,0:37:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.59,0:37:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.80,0:37:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.63,0:37:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.48,0:37:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.65,0:37:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.37,0:37:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.47,0:37:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝著我來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.48,0:37:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著機體還沒有流入他國 就先沉在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.13,0:37:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.23,0:37:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.67,0:37:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得趕緊離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.23,0:38:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.96,0:38:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在駕駛那東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.90,0:38:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.41,0:38:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒辦法像雷德那麼順手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.60,0:38:21.14,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,確認到操作機能顯著下降 請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.93,0:38:30.01,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.77,0:38:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣嗎？還是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.93,0:38:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.80,0:39:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣或許也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.56,0:39:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是部了不起的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.80,0:39:52.61,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認搭乘者的生體情報以及機體的損壞狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.35,0:39:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果很多部像你這樣的機械都能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.83,0:39:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切就都會亂套
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.19,0:40:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說是戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.70,0:40:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連生存之地都會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.87,0:40:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 我應該早點讓你回歸海底的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.10,0:40:14.04,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,將搭乘者認定為專屬駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.51,0:40:21.35,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,將機能維持更新為最優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.91,0:40:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.04,0:40:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.41,0:41:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.85,0:41:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾…Sys…tem
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.02,0:41:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.54,0:41:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是操作界面
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.70,0:41:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.80,0:42:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是馬茲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.57,0:42:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.17,0:42:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.30,0:42:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.76,0:42:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.85,0:42:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.78,0:42:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.76,0:42:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！你要做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.37,0:42:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.24,0:42:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.86,0:42:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.47,0:43:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.07,0:43:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.89,0:43:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.08,0:43:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.88,0:43:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 太好了 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.28,0:43:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那裡別動 我現在就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.37,0:43:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已經不能回到加爾剛蒂亞了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.05,0:43:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.97,0:43:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情變成這樣 都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.14,0:43:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個過錯是不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.11,0:43:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟這些沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.31,0:43:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就別管這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.56,0:43:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我而言 馬茲爾就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.98,0:44:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.18,0:44:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經沒有回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.57,0:44:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你很困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.10,0:44:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得得救了 你卻不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.70,0:44:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇 快帶莉瑪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.13,0:44:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要就此告辭 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.04,0:44:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇…誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.88,0:44:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那眼神 就像活著本身就已經是對你的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.29,0:44:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.50,0:44:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.84,0:44:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有接受這份罪行的覺悟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.59,0:44:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.20,0:45:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請允許我用這種方法贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.68,0:45:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.88,0:45:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.59,0:45:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為海洋只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.02,0:45:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.70,0:45:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 長期以來的修復工作真是辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.60,0:46:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 加爾剛蒂亞又增加了一個新的生活據點
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.65,0:46:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛我們所遭遇的身份不明的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.84,0:46:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是陸地國家所擁有的海上力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.92,0:46:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧護衛艦的奮鬥以及各位的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.78,0:46:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得受害情況縮減到了最低
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.02,0:46:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎來了新的船隻之後
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.25,0:46:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加爾剛蒂亞今後也必須是一個和平昌盛的艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.10,0:46:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 請各位助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.11,0:46:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架機體確實和這東西連接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.18,0:46:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這地球上還有我所不知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.92,0:46:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.60,0:46:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪出生在戰爭連連的陸地上
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.73,0:46:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怎樣生活下來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.41,0:46:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是懷著怎樣的心情看待我們的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.77,0:46:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.31,0:47:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.47,0:47:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪告訴過我 她不想破壞我們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.88,0:47:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管遇到怎樣的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.08,0:47:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都要在這裡生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.21,0:47:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在這裡保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.70,0:47:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
