Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:55.17,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}心の羽根ひろげ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:02:00.00,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕らは今日を生きていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:05.09,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}たとえどんな風が吹いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:09.27,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何度でも自由を求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:14.25,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}はばたいていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:18.61,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}悲しみを乗り越えた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:23.63,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}光があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:07.86,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}將聚散離合深埋心間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.74,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏出前進的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:21.88,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}記憶總以柔和的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:26.42,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}對我們報以微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:30.50,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天空的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.66,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}與濤聲的歌謠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:39.94,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自然而然的幸福滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:44.62,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們找到了開始的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:52.15,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}日出日落 冬去春來 世界不斷變遷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:55.17,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們張開心的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:02:00.00,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}度過一天又一天的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:05.09,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論面對怎樣的風向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:09.27,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始終朝著自由的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:14.25,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}振翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:18.61,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因為那悲傷的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:23.63,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}存在著綻放的光芒
